 and ethnographic material composed with a unique textual structure. The book is useful for those interested in Zionism and the Israeli-Palestinian conflict, as well in experimental writing styles.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAgriculture -- Israel -- Esdraelon, Plain of -- History -- 20th century. 0aAgriculture -- Palestine -- History -- 20th century. 0aAgriculture, Cooperative -- Palestine -- History -- 20th century. 0aCollective settlements -- Israel -- History -- 20th century. 0aJews -- Agriculture -- Israel -- Esdraelon, Plain of -- History -- 20th century. 0aJews -- Colonization -- Israel -- Esdraelon, Plain of -- History -- 20th century. 0aKibbutzim -- History. 7aHISTORY / Middle East / Israel & Palestine.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2013z978311102408008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAcademic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2015z97831106881460 cprintz978193484378940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978161811022040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781618110220423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781618110220/original  a978-3-11-068814-6  Academic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2015c2008d2015  a978-3-11-102408-0  Academic Studies Press Backlist eBook-Package 2008-2013c2008d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK